author: Darren Allan
title: Intel and AMD say they can cope with CPU demand in coronavirus chaos
description: Intel’s Pandemic Leadership Team is on the case, and AMD is well-positioned to maintain supply.
content:
Intel and AMD have both moved to reassure those who might be looking to buy CPUs consumers and businesses alike that supply wont run dry due to the coronavirus outbreak.
